 MBOMBELA – The annual Mr and Ms Bergvlam finale is a title all the entrants work hard to have and this year’s one was no exception. After an evening of entertainment and a showcase of the contestants’ creativity and achievements throughout the year, the moment came to announce this year’s winners. ALSO READ: Pieter Koen bring jolyt na Moving Mountains The crowd held its collective breath and, as the winners were announced, cheered wildly in celebration of their achievement. Mr and Ms Bergvlam 2019 was announced as Zandré van Niekerk and Bonolo Ranalana. The crowd erupted as the pair walked onstage and their crowning was a fitting end to an evening of spectacular entertainment.  